	   <tr><td colspan=2>Collect the pelts and sell the small tusks. The tusks are only worth around 3 gp, but with the pelts you can earn quite a lot pp. Bring them to Cappi Mctarnigal inside the bank building upstairs. Hand him 4 each time and you get some&nbsp;&nbsp;faction with the Rogues Guild, and pieces of Black Wolf Armor. Sell those to either vendors, or rogues for quick cash.<br><br>Good Luck<br>&nbsp;<br>Once there was a time when all people believed in God and the church ruled. This time is called the Dark Ages. </td></tr>
