	   <tr><td colspan=2>Check behind McQuad's Bar and Stout. If you were entering Halas and just crossed the lake hug the right wall. She should be behind The first building you come across.<br><br>As for levels, you can hang out in Blackburrow for your next few levels. Collect all gnoll fangs and give them into Captain Tillin at the warrior guild in South Qeynos for faction and good XP. (You can also take the moonstones he gives you for the fangs and hand them into McNeal Jocub at the Fish's Ale, also in South Qeynos near the docks. Though this results in faction and no real increase in XP)<br>&nbsp;<br>Zaviax McCleo <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=235432" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=235432</a><br><br>Vykore Mainsnoir <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=234170" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=234170</a><br><br>Shadow of the Dragon<br>Tunare<br>(www.eqsod.com)</td></tr>
