	   <tr><td colspan=2>You should be able to get a suit of banded for around 100pp.<br><br>My progression was:<br>&gt;Crappy leather (ruined pelts)<br><br>&gt;Banded (long time)<br><br>&gt;Imbued Northman Ringmail (I made it myself!&nbsp;&nbsp;WIS +2, STR +1, SvCold +2 each piece, better AC than Banded too)<br><br>&gt;Mob Drops, Bazaar purchases (anything with Wisdom)<br><br>The only piece of Totemic I bothered with was the Helmet, since it has +5 WIS.<br><br>Good luck!!<br>&nbsp;<br>______________________________________<br><b>Dargadin, Barbarian Shaman of the 55th Season</b><br>Darg&nbsp;&nbsp; 41 Barb Warrior<br>Cyrius 21 Eru Wizard<br><b><br>Ayonae Ro Server</b></td></tr>
