	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Charisma ONLY affects secondary resists for Charms and Mezzes.<br><br>There's been a LOT of debate about this, but I finally was able to ask the developers at FanFaire in San Francisco.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you want fewer resists, use your Malo line, but charisma won't help you at all as a Shaman unless you are using Charm Animal (or when you are buying your Alchemy herbs, of course).<br>&nbsp;<br>______________________________________<br><b>Dargadin, Barbarian Shaman of the 55th Season</b><br>Darg&nbsp;&nbsp; 41 Barb Warrior<br>Cyrius 21 Eru Wizard<br><b><br>Ayonae Ro Server</b></td></tr>
